==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Enlace
<hw>En*lace"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To bind or
encircle with lace, or as with lace; to lace; to encircle; to enfold;
hence, to entangle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Ropes of pearl her neck and breast <qex>enlace</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>P. Fletcher.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Enlacement</ent>⟦br⟧
